%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor BP as Business Partner

participant UI as Simulation UI
participant BFF as Project Planning BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant PPS as Project Planning Service
participant RCS as Resource Capacity Service
participant DB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}

BP->>UI: Open Schedule Simulation
UI->>BFF: Load estimate windows
BFF->>ORCH: Fetch estimates
ORCH->>PPS: Get PM/BP estimates
PPS->>DB: Read estimate rows
DB-->>PPS: Estimates
PPS-->>ORCH: Estimate response
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show estimate windows

BP->>UI: Select source and Execute
UI->>BFF: Run simulation
BFF->>ORCH: Start simulation flow
ORCH->>RCS: Compute earliest start and conflicts
RCS-->>ORCH: Simulation output
ORCH->>PPS: Save simulation result
PPS->>DB: Insert schedule_simulation and conflicts
PPS-->>ORCH: Saved result
ORCH-->>BFF: Simulation response
BFF-->>UI: Show earliest date and conflicts

BP->>UI: Enter dates and Submit
UI->>BFF: Submit proposed schedule
BFF->>ORCH: Start schedule submit flow
ORCH->>PPS: Save proposal and lock PM estimate entry
PPS->>DB: Update project_planning status = Awaiting CoE Approval
PPS->>DB: Set estimate_locked_flag = true
PPS->>DB: Insert schedule_approval
PPS-->>ORCH: Submission success
ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish ScheduleSubmitted Event
ORCH-->>BFF: Success
BFF-->>UI: Show submission confirmation
